{"id":232447314,"title":"【好書推薦】只為你寫的，沐家故事集","content":"# 只為你寫的，沐家故事集\n\n親子共讀，主角不一定只能是孩子，媽媽獲得的感動和力量，將成為孩子愛與夢想。這是一本送給孩子也送給媽媽的可愛故事集。\n\n作者在書背短短幾行文字，讓讀者想起屬於大人的心情~ 有多久沒有說故事給你愛的人和該被愛的自己聽了，讓這本書輕輕填滿你心中的某個缺口吧。\n\n童話裡躍出的魔法裁縫師、發光的小星星、不太一樣的大野狼、渴望幸福的孩子、愛作夢的恐龍，盛情邀約著大家走進屬於自己的篇章。\n\n第一本只為你寫的故事書，練習有一天把你的愛說出來。\n寫給你心裡那個還不想長大的小孩，無論你現在幾歲。\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/BQOh4nf.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/ARby7kt.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/mkvT8n6.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/eXcrTa3.jpg","excerpt":"# 只為你寫的，沐家故事集，親子共讀，主角不一定只能是孩子，媽媽獲得的感動和力量，將成為孩子愛與夢想。這是一本送給孩子也送給媽媽的可愛故事集。作者在書背短短幾行文字，讓讀者想起屬於大人的心情~ 有多久","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"e0a290f4-752b-48a2-a791-f211f8b46588","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-11-06T03:05:49.641Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-06T03:05:49.641Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":3,"tags":[],"topics":["繪本","書籍","創作"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"書籍","forumAlias":"book","school":"國立臺灣大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":3}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/BQOh4nf.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/ARby7kt.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/mkvT8n6.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/eXcrTa3.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"78894994-fc6e-4848-b622-63d088974022","url":"https://i.imgur.com/BQOh4nfl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/BQOh4nfl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/BQOh4nfl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-06T03:05:49.641Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-06T03:05:49.641Z"},{"id":"78894994-fc6e-4848-b622-63d088974022","url":"https://i.imgur.com/BQOh4nf.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/BQOh4nf","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/BQOh4nfl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"]